PARENT RESPONSE

Sent home a picture of kids working with this. Parents loved it. Several asked questions about specific animals. One parent sent photos from their vacation to Africa and we added them to our classroom collection.

Nice way to connect home and school.

---

PERSONAL NOTES

This took more time than I expected (finding good images was tedious) but was totally worth it. Kids use it constantly and actually learn the content.

Also it's expandable - I can keep adding animals as we learn about them. Not a "done and finished" material.

Sometimes I wish I'd started with simpler categories (farm animals vs zoo animals) before jumping to continents. But kids adapted fine.

